page.title: 09HOLY CROSS
page.content: We went to Holy Cross. Then we saw posh cars. We saw some birds and there were some old people there. There were some{houses.}They were nice because they were big probably with about 3 bedrooms and a big living room. The gardens were large and lots of the { {houses}had balconies and white spiral staircases. They also had large pathways about 50 yards long. The people we met were nice and seemed to like living there. I wouldn't like to have lived there because there were lots of retired people and very few young people.
